data.description: All brick home in the center of Newburgh is now on the market!  Tons of space in this home gives you plenty of room for your family.  The living room is at the front of the home, and leads into the open kitchen and dining area.  The dining room is graced by a beautiful stone wood-burning fireplace.  The kitchen has a large island and all appliances are included.  Down the hall you'll find two bedrooms and a full bath.  At the end of the hallway is the owners bedroom and another full bath.  The brand new luxury vinyl flooring will stand up to anything your kids or pets can dish out!  The home is located on a half acre lot.  There is also a patio off the dining room, and a fenced-in area for your furry friends.  The sellers are including a $649 2-10 home warranty.
